    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "王子一行人从艾缪尔的近卫兵口中\\n得知帝国的异变并赶往其同伴前去的村落，\\n却在那里遭到了神秘敌人的袭击。\\n在“心之怪盗团”的帮助下，\\n王子一行人最终脱身并与其一同撤退。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天前",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "尤蒂尔殿下，\\n初次见面。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "萨博亚",
            "context": "我叫萨博亚，是您的兄长……\\n艾缪尔大人的近卫兵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "艾缪尔！？\\n那个坏家伙的部下\\n来这里干什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "萨博亚",
            "context": "我深知身为敌对势力\\n不该向您寻求帮助，\\n但是……唔啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你有伤在身吗？\\n兰扎卜，快帮他治疗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好。有事就等到\\n伤治好之后再慢慢说吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "萨博亚",
            "context": "请、请等一下！\\n我还有另一位同伴为了告知\\n帝国的异变而去了附近的村落。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "萨博亚",
            "context": "唔唔……现在也许还来得及。\\n请一定要……救救……他……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，振作一点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "帝国的异变……\\n到底发生了什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "他说他的同伴\\n去了附近的村落对吧？\\n我们去打探一下情况吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "有道理。\\n我和卢卡去附近的村落一趟。\\n他就拜托你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好，这里就交给我吧。\\n你们要多加小心啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "啊，等等！我也去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂，尤蒂尔，\\n那边聚集了很多人啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可能发生了什么事。\\n我们去打听一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的男子",
            "context": "啊啊，艾缪尔大人！\\n艾缪尔大人您就是\\n我们活下去的动力……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村里的青年",
            "context": "全村一起歌颂艾缪尔大人吧！\\n要让更多的人们明白\\n艾缪尔大人的伟大才行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村落的女子",
            "context": "只有艾缪尔大人才能\\n给这片格拉斯迪亚大陆带来安宁！\\n啊啊，亲爱的艾缪尔大人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "这些人是怎么回事！？\\n一口一个艾缪尔大人……\\n这种狂热的样子绝对有问题！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "刚才那个人！\\n就是近卫兵说的同伴吧？\\n追他的那帮人是谁啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "唔！？怎、怎么还追过来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "住、住手！？哇啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "刚才是怎么回事！？好像有个\\n宝石一样的东西被从身体里取出……\\n到底发生了什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃……看来没时间考虑了。\\n小心点，他们要来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这是盯上我们了吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120213_01",
                "120213_01",
                "120213_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "暗影警卫Ａ",
            "context": "为了我们的王，\\n交出你们的“愿望”吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "该死，数量太多了……\\n怎么办，尤蒂尔，\\n要不要暂时撤退！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不能丢下倒下的士兵不管。\\n至少要想办法救下他！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120213_01",
                "120213_01",
                "120213_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "暗影警卫B",
            "context": "为了艾缪尔大人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "人变成了魔兽！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "呀、呀啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "纳姆！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "怎么回事！？\\n有人在攻击魔兽！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110379_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "魔兽？\\n这些家伙是暗影！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110380_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "暗影就是敌人。\\n我来对付它们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "毕竟不能丢下\\n有困难的人不管嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你、你们到底是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110377_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我们是——“心之怪盗团”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "心之……怪盗团！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110377_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "这里就交给我们吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "好、好厉害……\\n他们到底是何方神圣……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110377_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "到此为止了。\\n现身吧，亚森！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110379_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "JOKER，真有你的！\\n这下附近的暗影\\n差不多都除干净了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110380_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "但是马上就会有\\n新的敌人赶来增援。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "JOKER，怎么办？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110377_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "嗯……先撤退吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110379_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "是啊。喂，你们几个，\\n不想被夺走愿望的话，\\n就跟吾辈们一起走吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "愿、愿望？跟你们一起……\\n是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110378_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "就是说……总之眼下\\n先和我们一起逃跑吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哦，好的。不过，在那之前\\n我想救倒下的士兵……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110380_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "抱歉……已经来不及了。\\n我刚才看到他的愿望\\n已经被别的暗影夺走了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶……来不及了……\\n是指死了的意思吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110379_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "这个嘛……倒也不是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "啊啊，艾缪尔大人……\\n艾缪尔大人……万岁！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "太好了，原来他没事啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "没事倒是好……\\n但他看起来不太对劲啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110380_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "他被“心牢” 的“王”\\n夺走了“愿望”，\\n已经“悔改”了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110380_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "不夺回愿望的话，\\n就没法恢复原样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "什么乱七八糟的……\\n又是心牢又是王，还有愿望……\\n你们到底是什么人？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110379_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "之后再向你解释。\\n现在不抓紧时间的话，\\n暗影又会聚起来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110377_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "要赶在被包围前撤出去，\\n我们走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们也一起走吧！\\n退到安全的地方之后，\\n再向他们打听这事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20429_02_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}